                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成4点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素伤害</span>，</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">启途誓使</span>的[凭依]级数+2。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/03/47826599/b6ab0891aede70ddf48bfa3859de14ea_567961897876001664.png",
